   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "> The key thing to remember about regular expressions is that they are almost read forwards and backwards at the same time. \n",
    "> 几乎是从前往后读的同时也从后往前读。\n",
    "\n"
   ]
